\c 11
\s UAthaliya uzibeka abe ngumbusi
\p
\v 1 UAthaliya unina kaAhaziya\x + 8.26. Hlu. 9.5.\x* esebonile ukuthi indodana yakhe ifile, wasukuma wachitha yonke inzalo yesikhosini\x + 2 Lan. 22.10. 24.1.\x*.
\v 2 Kodwa uJehosheba indodakazi yenkosi uJoramu, udadewabo kaAhaziya, wathatha uJowashi indodana kaAhaziya, wameba phakathi kwamadodana enkosi abulawayo, yena lomlizane wakhe ekamelweni lokulala. Basebemfihla ebusweni bukaAthaliya ukuze angabulawa.
\v 3 Wayelaye-ke efihliwe endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* iminyaka eyisithupha; uAthaliya wasebusa phezu kwelizwe.
\p
\v 4 Ngomnyaka wesikhombisa uJehoyada wasethuma wathatha izinduna zamakhulu\x + 11.9. 2 Lan. 22.11.\x*, lamaKariti\x + 11.19. 2 Sam. 20.23.\x* kanye labalindi\x + 10.25. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*, wabaletha kuye endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*. Wenza isivumelwano labo, wabafungisa endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, wabatshengisa indodana yenkosi.
\v 5 Wasebalaya esithi: Nansi into elizayenza: Ingxenye eyodwa kwezintathu yenu elingena ngesabatha izakuba ngabalindi bomlindo wendlu yenkosi\x + 1 Lan. 9.25.\x*,
\v 6 lengxenye eyodwa kwezintathu izakuba sesangweni leSuri\x + 2 Lan. 23.5.\x*, lengxenye eyodwa kwezintathu esangweni ngemva kwabalindi\x + 10.25. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*; ngokunjalo lizalinda umlindo wendlu, ingafohlelwa.
\v 7 Lengxenye ezimbili zenu lonke eliphuma ngesabatha, bona bazagcina umlindo wendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* mayelana lenkosi\x + 1 Lan. 9.25.\x*.
\v 8 Lizazingelezela inkosi inhlangothi zonke, ngulowo lalowo elezikhali esandleni sakhe\x + 6.14.\x*; lozangena kokuhleliweyo uzabulawa\x + 11.15. 1 Kho. 6.9.\x*. Libe lenkosi ekuphumeni kwayo lekungeneni kwayo\x + Nani 27.17.\x*.
\v 9 Induna zamakhulu zasezisenza njengakho konke uJehoyada umpristi akulayayo; zathatha, yileyo laleyo abantu bayo abangena ngesabatha lalabo abaphuma ngesabatha, zafika kuJehoyada umpristi\x + 1 Lan. 9.25.\x*.
\v 10 Umpristi wasenika izinduna zamakhulu imikhonto lezihlangu ezazingezenkosi uDavida ezazisendlini yeN\nd kosi\x + 1 Lan. 18.7. 2 Sam. 8.7.\x*\nd*.
\v 11 Abalindi basebesima, ngulowo lalowo elezikhali esandleni sakhe, kusukela kwesokunene sendlu kusiya kwesokhohlo sendlu, ngaselathini langasendlini, enkosini inhlangothi zonke\x + 10.25. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*.
\v 12 Waseyikhupha indodana yenkosi, wayethesa umqhele\x + 2 Sam. 1.10.\x*, \add wayinika\add* ubufakazi; bayibeka yaba yinkosi, bayigcoba, batshaya izandla, basebesithi: Kayiphile inkosi\x + Eks. 25.16. 31.18. Dute. 17.18.\x*!
\p
\v 13 UAthaliya esizwa umsindo wabalindi \add lo\add*wabantu waya ebantwini endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*;
\v 14 wabona, khangela-ke, inkosi yayimi ngasensikeni njengomkhuba, lezinduna labavutheli bezimpondo bengasenkosini\x + 23.3. 2 Lan. 34.31.\x*, labantu bonke belizwe bethokoza bavuthela izimpondo\x + 1 Kho. 1.34.\x*. UAthaliya wasedabula izigqoko zakhe, wamemeza wathi: Ugobe! Ugobe\x + Gen. 44.13.\x*!
\v 15 UJehoyada umpristi waselaya induna zamakhulu, abaphathi bebutho\x + Nani 31.14. 2 Lan. 23.14.\x*, wathi kubo: Mkhupheleni ngaphandle kokuhleliweyo\x + 11.15. 1 Kho. 6.9.\x*, lomlandelayo limbulale ngenkemba. Ngoba umpristi wathi: Kangabulawelwa endlini kaJehova.
\v 16 Basebembamba ngezandla, wasehamba ngendlela yokungena kwamabhiza endlini yenkosi, wabulawelwa khonapho\x + 2 Lan. 23.15.\x*.
\p
\v 17 UJehoyada wasesenza isivumelwano phakathi kukaJehova lenkosi labantu ukuthi babe ngabantu bakaJehova\x + Josh. 24.25.\x*; laphakathi kwenkosi labantu\x + 2 Sam. 5.3.\x*.
\v 18 Bonke abantu belizwe basebengena endlini kaBhali, bayidilizela phansi\x + 10.21,26.\x*; amalathi akhe lezithombe zakhe baziphahlaza ngokupheleleyo, loMathani umpristi kaBhali bambulala phambi kwamalathi\x + Dute. 12.3.\x*. Umpristi wasebeka abaphathi phezu kwendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 19 Wasethatha izinduna zamakhulu lamaKariti labalindi labo bonke abantu belizwe, bayehlisa inkosi isuka endlini kaJehova\x + 11.4.\x*, beza ngendlela yesango labalindi endlini yenkosi. Yasihlala esihlalweni sobukhosi samakhosi\x + 11.6. 2 Lan. 23.20.\x*.
\v 20 Bonke abantu belizwe basebethokoza. Umuzi wasusiba lokuthula, sebembulele uAthaliya ngenkemba \add ngase\add*ndli\add ni\add* yenkosi.
\v 21 UJehowashi wayeleminyaka eyisikhombisa lapho esiba yinkosi.